body.description: Chrome Battery presents YB14A-A2 sealed AGM batteries, the precision power solution. Each battery is constructed with lead calcium alloy and absorbed glass mat technology that allows for a complete maintenance-free and high-performance operation. Chrome Battery features improvements in the longevity, warranty, returns, and shipping over our other brands; Pirate and Zipp. All YB14A-A2 Chrome Battery brand AGM batteries are manufactured with the highest quality materials and rigorously tested to ensure safety, OEM compatibility, effectiveness, and optimal performance. YB14A-A2 is a 12V 19CCA High Performance Sealed AGM Battery. YB14A-A2 has AGM Separators for superior design and durability.YB14A-A2 Battery Features: No spills, no leaks, and no water to check. Extreme vibration resistance to ensure maximum conductivity. High Cranking Amps & Low Self-Discharge Rate. Fully charged, ready for immediate use. Fits in a variety of applications, ranging from motorcycles, ATVs, UTVs, jet skis, snowmobiles, scooters and more. YB14A-A2 AGM Battery Specifications: Model: YB14A-A2 Dimensions: (H) 6.57" x (L) 5.31" (W) 3.54" Weight: 1.16 lbs.Volts: 12V Polarity: [+ -]Condition: New. Also Replaces: YTX14AH-BS, UTX14AH-BS, PTX14AH-BS, BTX14AH-BS, CYTX14AH-BS, ES14AH-BS, ETX15, M62H4A, CTX14H-BS FA, YUAM62H4A, YUAM72H4A, FS-14AH-BS, MBTX14AU.
